    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>状态设计</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "设 <code>dp[t][i][j]</code>：时刻 <code>t</code> 恰好到达 <code>(i,j)</code> 的方案数。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>转移</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "从上一时刻 <code>t-1</code> 的所有可能前驱转移来——即同一列上方任意行，或同一行左侧任意列。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "朴素枚举前驱是 <code>O(k * n * m * (n+m))</code>，显然需要优化。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>前缀和优化</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$\ndp[t][i][j] = \\sum_{r=1}^{i-1} dp[t-1][r][j] \\;+\\; \\sum_{c=1}^{j-1} dp[t-1][i][c]\n$$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这就是典型的<strong>二维前缀和加速</strong>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<code>pre_down[i][j]</code>：列方向前缀和，即 <code>(1,j)~(i,j)</code> 的 <code>dp[t-1]</code> 之和",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<code>pre_right[i][j]</code>：行方向前缀和，即 <code>(i,1)~(i,j)</code> 的 <code>dp[t-1]</code> 之和",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "于是每个状态的转移变成 <code>O(1)</code>：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<code>dp[i][j] = pre_down[i-1][j] + pre_right[i][j-1]</code>",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>滚动 + 维度交换</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "你一开始按 <code>(i,j,t)</code> 三维顺序跑，发现 <code>dp[505][505][105]</code> 会 MLE（约 2.6e7 个 int，约 100MB 以上）。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "但你很快意识到：<code>dp[t]</code> 只依赖 <code>dp[t-1]</code>，<strong>可以滚动</strong>。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "然而按 <code>(i,j,t)</code> 顺序写滚动时，前缀和不易维护（因为需要完整的上一个时刻的二维信息）。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "于是你改成 <strong><code>(t,i,j)</code> 外层按时间滚动</strong>，每层重新计算 <code>dp[][]</code> 和 <code>pre[][]</code>，空间降到 <code>O(n*m)</code>。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "ll dp[505][505], pre[2][505][505];\nbool vis[505][505][105];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n, m, q, k; cin >> n >> m >> q >> k;\n\tfa(i, 0, n)fa(j, 0, m)fa(k, 0, 1)dp[i][j] = pre[k][i][j] = 0;\n\tfa(i, 0, n)fa(j, 0, m)fa(t, 0, k)vis[i][j][t] = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, q) {\n\t\tint x, y, t; cin >> x >> y >> t;\n\t\tvis[x][y][t] = 1;\n\t}\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, 1, m)fa(t, 1, k)if (vis[i][j][t - 1])vis[i][j][t] = 1;\n\tdp[1][1] = 1;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tif (vis[i][1][1])continue;\n\t\tpre[0][i][1] = (pre[0][i - 1][1] + dp[i][1]) % mod;\n\t}\n\tfa(j, 1, m) {\n\t\tif (vis[1][j][1])continue;\n\t\tpre[1][1][j] = (pre[1][1][j - 1] + dp[1][j]) % mod;\n\t}\n\tll mn = 0, ans = 0;\n \tfa(t, 2, k + 1) {\n\t\tfa(i, 0, n)fa(j, 0, m)dp[i][j] = 0;\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, 1, m) {\n\t\t\tdp[i][j] = (dp[i][j] + pre[0][i - 1][j]) % mod;\n\t\t\tdp[i][j] = (dp[i][j] + pre[1][i][j - 1]) % mod;\n\t\t}\n\t\tif (dp[n][m] and !mn)mn = t;\n\t\tans = (ans + dp[n][m]) % mod;\n\t\tfa(i, 0, n)fa(j, 0, m)fa(k, 0, 1)pre[k][i][j] = 0;\n\t\tfa(j, 1, m)fa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\t\tif (vis[i][j][t])continue;\n\t\t\tpre[0][i][j] = (pre[0][i - 1][j] + dp[i][j]) % mod;\n\t\t}\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, 1, m) {\n\t\t\tif (vis[i][j][t])continue;\n\t\t\tpre[1][i][j] = (pre[1][i][j - 1] + dp[i][j]) % mod;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tif (!mn)cout << -1 << endl;\n\telse cout << ans << ' ' << mn - 1 << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
